</p><p class="- topic/p ">Follow the instruction on the screen. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place a round object in the middle of the engine between the buffer plate and the guide plate. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The led of the media drawer is the middle of the engine. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-C063EDA3-A82B-4E23-890C-E7F8EE8453FA" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not damage the guide plate, buffer plate or the anti static brush, 
